#### **3. Structure Your Repository**

Cloud-Security-Projects/
│
├── README.md  # Overview of all projects
├── Secure-VPC-Project/  # Folder for each project
│   ├── vpc-setup.md  # Detailed description of VPC setup steps
│   ├── vpc-config.yaml  # VPC configuration file if using IaC
│   └── diagrams/  # Include any diagrams (e.g., network architecture)
│
├── IAM-RBAC-Project/  
│   ├── iam-roles.md  # Details on IAM roles and policies
│   ├── iam-config.json  # Sample IAM configuration file
│
├── Encryption-Storage-Project/  
│   ├── storage-encryption.md  # Encryption process for storage
│   ├── s3-config.yaml  # Example configurations for S3 or Blob
│
└── Intrusion-Detection-Project/
    ├── ids-setup.md  # Setup guide for IDS (GuardDuty or Azure Security)
    └── response-automation.py  # Lambda function for automatic incident response
